Anh - Anh
paperhanger
■ noun a person who decorates with wallpaper, especially professionally.

sentences.en: My boss keeps me as busy as a one - armed paperhanger.
sentences.vi: Sếp tôi cứ giao việc cho tôi suốt.

sentences.en: I have got plenty of work, I am busy as a one-armed paperhanger.
sentences.vi: Tôi có hàng tá việc. Tôi lúc nào cũng đầu tắt mặt tối.
